"This form is for small building projects such as building an addition, demolishing a structure, or building a detached building under 70m2 where no one will live or stay. The applicant must provide details of the project, including dimensions, and indicate if any special permissions are needed. The applicant must also follow building regulations and obtain necessary permits. The form includes sections for property details, contact information, municipal plans, building size calculations, distance measurements, potential conflicts with surroundings, and required attachments such as drawings and neighbor notifications. The applicant must sign the form before submitting it to the municipality for approval.En tillatelse er gitt for oppf\u00f8ring av en frittst\u00e5ende dobbelgarasje p\u00e5 eiendommen til Helge Botnmark. Tillatelsen inkluderer vilk\u00e5r som m\u00e5 oppfylles, og det er informasjon om klagefrist og prosedyrer for ferdigattest. Nabovarsel har blitt sendt ut, og det er vurdert at tiltaket er i samsvar med gjeldende plangrunnlag. Gebyret for tillatelsen er ogs\u00e5 spesifisert.Helge Botnmark has sent a revised application for a garage construction after receiving a rejection notice due to previous deficiencies. The application has been edited based on feedback received from a phone call with the building department. Botnmark is open to addressing any further deficiencies and hopes for a positive response.Adresse: R\u00e5dhusgata 2, 9008 Troms\u00f8 \nPostadresse: Postboks 6900 Langnes, 9299 Troms\u00f8 \nTelefon: 77 79 00 00 \nE-post: postmottak@tromso.kommune.no \nOrg.nr.: 940 101 808 \nNettside: tromso.kommune.no \n\nDet er sendt ut et varsel om avslag p\u00e5 s\u00f8knad om oppf\u00f8ring av en dobbelgarasje p\u00e5 Njords veg 41. S\u00f8knaden er mottatt 23.05.2022 og etter vurdering anses tiltaket i tr\u00e5d med reguleringsplanen og kommuneplanens arealdel. S\u00f8knaden krever imidlertid en dispensasjon fordi m\u00f8neh\u00f8yden p\u00e5 dobbelgarasjen overskrider det maksimale tillatte i kpa. bestemmelse pkt. 8.6. Dispensasjonss\u00f8knader krever en begrunnelse i henhold til plan- og bygningsloven.\n\nS\u00f8knaden for garasjen utenfor byggegrensen krever dispensasjon fra reguleringsplanen og m\u00e5 ta hensyn til maksimalt tillatt tomteutnyttelsesgrad p\u00e5 30% BYA. Det er ogs\u00e5 viktig \u00e5 inkludere areal avsatt til parkering i beregningen. En grov estimat tyder p\u00e5 at tomteutnyttelsesgraden allerede kan v\u00e6re over 30% BYA, og det m\u00e5 derfor redegj\u00f8res for dette i s\u00f8knaden og eventuelt s\u00f8kes om dispensasjon hvis tomteutnyttelsesgraden overskrides.\n\nHelge Botnmark has applied for permission to build a double garage on his property at Njords veg 41. The application is currently under review and may require a dispensation from height regulations for double garages. The proposed garage meets the zoning regulations for residential purposes but may need further approval for its height. All dispensation requests must be justified and require a reasoned application.\n\nA garage is being proposed outside the building boundary in the zoning plan, so a dispensation from the building boundary towards the municipal road \"Njords veg\" is required. The area in question is designated for business use with a maximum building density of 35%, but since the project does not involve new residential lots or units, the maximum density allowed is 30%. Parking spaces must also be included in the building density calculation, with specific requirements for resident and guest parking. An estimate suggests that the current building density on the lot is already over 30%, so if this is confirmed, a dispensation will need to be sought. Detailed drawings of the existing buildings are required to clarify the building density on the lot.\n\nThe application for building a garage is dependent on dispensation for building boundary, height requirements for double garages, and potential exceeding of maximum plot utilization. This information must be included in the notice to neighbors, along with details on any potential exceeding of limits. Feedback from a neighboring property opposes a closer placement than 4m, but for buildings under 50m\u00b2, they can be placed within 1m without neighbor consent. The distance from the proposed garage to neighboring properties and regulated road areas must be specified. The municipality determines that dispensation for maximum ridge height cannot be granted, and it appears that the plot has already exceeded the maximum plot utilization limit, making a dispensation unlikely. The municipality informs of the rejection of the application for a garage construction with dispensations for maximum ridge height, building boundary, and potential plot utilization exceeding. They do not see that the benefits of granting dispensation outweigh the drawbacks.\n\nS\u00f8knaden forventes \u00e5 bli avsl\u00e5tt i henhold til plan- og bygningsloven og kommunens arealplan, samt avstandskravet til vei. Dette varselet om avslag er ikke et endelig vedtak som kan p\u00e5klages. Dispensasjon kan kun gis dersom visse vilk\u00e5r er oppfylt, blant annet at fordelene klart oppveier ulempene, og hensynene bak bestemmelsen ikke blir vesentlig tilsidesatt. Selv om disse vilk\u00e5rene er oppfylt, betyr det ikke n\u00f8dvendigvis at dispensasjon vil bli innvilget.\n\nKommunen har frihet til \u00e5 gi dispensasjon for \u00e5 overskride bestemte regler knyttet til garasjeprosjektet. S\u00f8knaden om \u00e5 bygge en garasje med en h\u00f8ydeoverskridelse p\u00e5 0,205m er vurdert i forhold til regler om tomteutnyttelse og uteareal. Kommunen mener fordelene ved \u00e5 gi dispensasjon ikke veier opp for ulempene, og anmoder at s\u00f8knaden trekkes. Hvis ikke, kan den behandles, men avslag er sannsynlig. Naboer er varslet om s\u00f8knaden og en naboeiendom har uttrykt motstand mot plasseringen av garasjen. Avstanden til naboeiendom og vei m\u00e5 spesifiseres i s\u00f8knaden.\n\nKommunen vurderer s\u00f8knaden om oppf\u00f8ring av en garasje og dispensasjon fra krav om maksimal m\u00f8neh\u00f8yde, byggegrenser og tomteutnyttelse. Et varsel om avslag er sendt, da fordelene ved \u00e5 innvilge dispensasjon ikke anses \u00e5 v\u00e6re st\u00f8rre enn ulempene. S\u00f8knaden er mangelfull og tiltakshaver m\u00e5 avklare flere punkter og s\u00f8ke om flere dispensasjoner. Det bes om tilbakemelding innen en frist, ellers vil saken tas til behandling. Gebyr vil p\u00e5l\u00f8pe ved behandling av s\u00f8knaden. Henvendelser kan rettes til saksbehandlerne oppgitt i brevet.Helge Botnmark has applied for a permit to build a double garage on his property at Njords veg 41 in Troms\u00f8. The initial application was received on May 23, 2022, and there was a subsequent notice of rejection on June 22, 2022. After reviewing the application, it was determined that the proposed construction aligns with the zoning regulations of the \"Universitetsomr\u00e5de II Gimle Nyg\u00e5rd\" and the municipal plan for residential purposes. As a result, no further dispensation is required under the Planning and Building Act.\n\nIn the response letter from the applicant, the following deficiencies were clarified and changes to the proposed project were made:\n- The proposed garage's ridge height was reduced to 5m.\n- The stated eaves height was reduced to 2.345m, but the correct eaves height for the project is estimated to be about 4m.\n- The distance from the proposed garage to the regulated road area is within the requirements specified in the regulations.\n- The distance from the proposed project to the residential house is within the requirements.\n- The loft in the proposed garage will be used for storage, not as a living space.\n- The existing garage will be demolished when the new garage is in place.\n- The garage tent has been confirmed to be removed.\nAs a result of the clarification of the above deficiencies, the requirement for a waiver of the ridge height and plot ratio has been waived. However, a dispensation is still needed for the eaves height, as it exceeds the maximum allowed height for garages in the area. Additionally, a dispensation is required for the building boundary towards the municipal road, as the proposed garage extends beyond it.\n\nDispensasjonss\u00f8knader m\u00e5 begrunnes og krever en grunngitt s\u00f8knad i henhold til plan- og bygningsloven. S\u00f8knad om dispensasjon fra byggegrensen mot vei foreligger ikke. Alle dispensasjonss\u00f8knader m\u00e5 inkluderes i nabovarselet. En forel\u00f8pig tilbakemelding p\u00e5 en s\u00f8knad om oppf\u00f8ring av garasje p\u00e5 eiendommen Njords veg 41 indikerer at tiltaket er i tr\u00e5d med reguleringsplanen og kommuneplanens arealdel, og derfor ikke krever dispensasjon. S\u00f8ker/tiltakshaver gjorde endringer p\u00e5 oms\u00f8kt tiltak i svarbrevet, blant annet redusert m\u00f8neh\u00f8yde og gesimsh\u00f8yde.\n\nOppgitte m\u00e5linger for gesimsh\u00f8yde, avstand til veiareal og bolighus er korrekte og innenfor kravene. Loftet i garasjen benyttes ikke til varig opphold, den eksisterende garasjen skal rives n\u00e5r den nye er p\u00e5 plass, og garasjeteltet er fjernet. Dispensasjon fra m\u00f8neh\u00f8yde og tomteutnyttelsesgrad er ikke lenger n\u00f8dvendig. S\u00f8knaden om dispensasjon for gesimsh\u00f8yde og byggegrense mot kommunalveg er fortsatt n\u00f8dvendig og m\u00e5 begrunnes i henhold til plan- og bygningsloven. Dispensasjonss\u00f8knad for byggegrense mot veg mangler forel\u00f8pig.\n\nKommunen varsler om avslag p\u00e5 en s\u00f8knad om oppf\u00f8ring av garasje med dispensasjon fra maks tillatte gesimsh\u00f8yde og byggegrense veg. De vurderer at fordelene ved \u00e5 innvilge dispensasjon ikke veier tyngre enn ulempene, og anmoder s\u00f8keren om \u00e5 trekke s\u00f8knaden eller gj\u00f8re endringer. S\u00f8knaden vil trolig bli avvist i henhold til lover og regler. Det er gitt en frist for tilbakemelding, og gebyrer vil p\u00e5l\u00f8pe ved behandling av s\u00f8knaden. Henvendelser kan rettes til saksbehandlerne oppgitt i brevet.A ferdigattest has been approved for the construction of a detached double garage on Njords veg 41, in the name of Helge Botnmark. The approval includes a condition for the existing garage on the property to be demolished to meet certain requirements, but this condition has been deemed invalid by the municipality. The decision can be appealed to the Statsforvalteren in Troms and Finnmark within three weeks.The document is a building quality application for approval of completion of work in accordance with Pbl \u00a7 21-10, SAK10 \u00a7\u00a7 8-1 and 8-2. It includes a checklist for minor remaining tasks, confirmation of compliance with requirements, documentation of non-permit changes, and submission of final waste report. The application also requires information on heating systems, energy supply, and submission of necessary documentation for the operational phase. The responsible applicant must ensure the final report is updated and stored.Helge Botnmark is sending a revised garage construction application to the Troms\u00f8 municipality after receiving a rejection due to deficiencies in the previous application. He has made edits based on feedback and is open to addressing any further deficiencies. He hopes for a positive response."